Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wet my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The mission to confirm maintenance,\Nto the HQ-command line,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for high-level emergency situations."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's quite a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail, we could\Nall be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under certain conditions,\Na level-one warning is issued,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all forces in the area are placed\Non emergency standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of mission is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You watch the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this phone is our hotline\Nto the capital's HQ, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it ever rung?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it would be bad if it rang,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it would be even worse\Nif it didn't ring when it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So once every six months, they run a test to ensure it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we call that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember it, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The command communications line\Nfor high-level... What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's the command communications\Nline for the high-level...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission to confirm maintenance,\Nto the HQ command line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for high-level emergency situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes, {\i1}yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try\Ntalking on the telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It works in more or less the same way\Nas the Takemikazuchi's intercom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that the distance\Nis a bit further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk to people\Nreally far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's kind of strange to talk\Nto someone you can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you get used\Nto it, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the issue is that we don't know\Nwhen it'll happen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you watch the phone\Nthe entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Sorami Kanata of the\N1121 Platoon, Helvetian Republic Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:05:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the call ends,\Nyou replace the receiver on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fi-Fi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to rush some\Ndocuments to HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claus comes next\Nweek, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm off to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the phone, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do it right, they might think\Nwe've actually been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not... Not asleep at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hangar again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, what do you\Nwant for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do both you and Kureha
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,try to keep me from the kitchen,\Neven when it's my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to cook all the time\Nbefore you two came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should taste fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It doesn't taste as\Nbad as it looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's got a very strong\Ntaste! It's fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go at it even\Nharder than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, it's Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to stay by the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got a visitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any more sandwiches\Nmixed with cutting board...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made at the farm where we\Nusually get our apple juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are related to\Nour calvados, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... She found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can give these two\Nas gifts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, there's a merchant's\Nguild's meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They help us out with a lot of things,\Nso from time to time, we give them presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They tried their\Nhardest to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you sometime, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to eat\Nlunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants a real explanation\Nfrom the military
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the news in this\Nweek's papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how the peace treaty conferences\Naren't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're working out the reparations\Nand territorial lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural that it would drag on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, the old guild guys\Nwant to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gained a lot more fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you played a Flame Maiden\Nat the water-throwing festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their numbers have\Nbeen growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, yeah. I've gotta go to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm a Fortress Maiden,\Nheart and soul, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will complete my mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. It's in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I'll give these to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that they're so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are trumpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are fabulous, wonderful,\Nfabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sounding better\Nwith the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a present for\Npracticing so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll keep you awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C... D... E... F... G...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess summer's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The laundry's gonna get wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The courtyard's within the\Ntheater of operations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad your laundry is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I-I'm sorry to\Nask you for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for visiting so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to return to Treize tomorrow,\Nso I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to say\Ngoodbye to soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard he's been less than polite\Nto people from your base.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to apologize\Nfor that, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, too? The black-haired one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your book?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for the uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,command communications line...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for high-level HQ emergency situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're waiting for this to ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never used one\Nbefore, so I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure that I'll do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Yumina is also attending\Nthe guild meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's going to get donations\Nfrom the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? You have some too, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll drink your stupid cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't think you can\Nbuy me off with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you two guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make it for the kids,\N'cause kids love phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Hello," first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always say that\Non the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can really hear his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Sorami Kanata of the\N1121 Platoon, Helvetia Republic Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm honored to receive\Nthis phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The phone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is the priest and our...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gods! How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to thank them for everything\Nthey'd done and to say goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but instead, you messed around\Nand caused trouble for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your clothes are soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I have a change...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How brilliant you look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you, Yumina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash and return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You can keep them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too big for the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't imagine anyone looking\Nas good as you in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you play with us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe if I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May all blessings be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. I need to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wet my pants...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, those old guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kana-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wet my pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, you'll get sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was holding it in\Nthis whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll really do whatever she's told.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't get it...\NI can't move at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she fails at timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Master Sergeant Rio Kazumiya of\Nthe 1121 Platoon of the Helvetia Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard we were confirming your line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I insisted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You simply haven't forgiven me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this time,\Nwhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I want you to save this\Ncountry... Save Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:22:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, surely you haven't\Nbeen in there the whole day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I sleep well there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute, Kana!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing\Nin the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata fell and can't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a spoiled girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,A Typhoon Passes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Illusion and Reality.
